title: Anthony Albanese | Australia, Biography, Age, & Wife | Britannica
snippet: Anthony Albanese (born March 2, 1963, Sydney, New South Wales, Australia) is an Australian politician who became the 31st prime minister of Australia in May 2022 at the head of the first Labor government to rule the country since 2013.
